Frontend:
- Framework: React
- Language: TypeScript
- Styling: TailwindCSS
- State Management: Zustand

Backend:
- Framework: FastAPI
- Language: Python 3.11+
- Database: PostgreSQL
- ORM: SQLModel

Tooling:
- Linting: ESLint + Prettier (frontend), ruff + black (backend)
- Package Managers: npm (frontend), poetry (backend)
- Future integrations: TBD (AI, APIs, health data sources)
